attributionInfo.brokerName: PREMIER REAL ESTATE OF THE SANDHILLS LLC

data.description: No HOA! The 1.5 story ranch styled home rests in a cul-de-sac in the Dove Field subdivision (Hoke Co.). Walk inside to find no carpet throughout the first floor along with 3 spacious bedrooms and 2 full bathrooms. The second floor is home to a cozy bonus area or can be used as a 4th bedroom. With almost half an acre of land, there are endless ways to spend time in the fenced backyard! Heating/Air units were replaced in 2021. Dishwasher/stove are less than 12 months old. Jack Britt district! Refrigerator conveys with property.
